description:
Bobby explains why he came in on being off today. He woke up at 1am last night and couldn’t fall back asleep. Mike D talks about getting his marriage license in Texas over the weekend and his fiancé’s parents meeting for the first time. Bobby also talks about Caitlin trying to drink a gallon of water a day.
